  "steps": [
    "Take the swab (NP or OP)",
    "Insert swab into Tube H with lysis buffer ( 500 µL , consisiting of 2 Molarity (M) Guanidine Thiocyanate Fisher Scientific Catalog #BP221 50 millimolar (mM) TCEP-HCl Gold Biotechnology Catalog #TCEP 25 millimolar (mM) Sodium citrate P212121 0.02 µg/µL Glycogen Thermo Scientific Catalog #AM9510 and pH 8 - pH 9 ) 00:00:30, violent shaking 00:04:30, Incubation",
