    "Discard supernatant after pulling the particles to the side",
    "Add 400 µL, EtOH , resuspend",
    "Discard supernatant after pulling the particles to the side",
    "Add 400 µL, EtOH , resuspend",
    "Discard supernatant after pulling the particles to the side",
    "Add 40 µL, RNAse free water , resuspend",
    "Pull the particles to the side and take supernatant to load the chip as described"
